    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Stiff cardboard faced with decorative paper, foil, or cloth, sometimes also having a textured surface; used for matting two-dimensional art work or documents.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
